olor: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">sudo apt </span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #2e95d3; background: #F7F7F8;\">update</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">安装 MariaDB：</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 9.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">sudo apt install mariadb-server <br /></span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">这将安装 MariaDB 数据库服务器和客户端。</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; background: #F7F7F8;\">启动 MariaDB 服务：</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">sudo systemctl </span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #2e95d3; background: #F7F7F8;\">start</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">mariadb </span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; background: #F7F7F8;\">设置 MariaDB 自动启动：</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">sudo systemctl </span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #d7890b; background: #F7F7F8;\">enable</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">mariadb <br /></span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">这将在系统启动时自动启动 MariaDB 服务。</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; background: #F7F7F8;\">验证 MariaDB 安装：</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; background: #F7F7F8;\">sudo mysql_secure_installation <br /></span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; background: #F7F7F8;\">按照提示输入 MariaDB root 用户的密码，并回答其他问题。这将帮助您设置 MariaDB 的一些基本安全设置。</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .375in; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\">完成上述步骤后，您的 Ubuntu 20.04 系统中应该已经安装了 MariaDB 数据库，并且可以使用 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysql</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 命令行客户端来连接和操作数据库。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\" type=\"1\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\" value=\"2\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\">要在</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\"> </span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\">Ubuntu 中安装 MariaDB 的开发库（</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\">mariadb-devel</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\">），您可以执行以下命令：</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .375in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 9.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .375in; font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #979797;\">sudo apt install libmariadb-dev</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .375in; font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"background: #F7F7F8;\">这将安装 MariaDB 的开发库和头文件，以便您可以编译和链接使用 MariaDB 的程序。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .375in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\" type=\"1\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\" value=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\">然后启动数据库并设置开机自启</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">systemctl restart mariadb</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">systemctl enable mariadb</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\" type=\"1\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\" value=\"4\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: norma