\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"background: #F7F7F8;\">如果您想查看特定用户的权限，请执行以下 SQL 命令：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: inherit; color: #2e95d3;\">SHOW</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; color: #2e95d3;\"> </span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: inherit; color: #979797;\">GRANTS </span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: inherit; color: #2e95d3;\">FOR</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; color: #2e95d3;\"> </span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: inherit; color: #979797;\">username; </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\">其中 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">username</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 是要查看其权限的用户的名称。这将显示给定用户的权限列表，包括它们对哪些数据库和表具有哪些权限。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\" type=\"1\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\" value=\"7\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\">要导出 MariaDB 数据库的数据和 SQL，您可以使用 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysqldump</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 命令。</span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysqldump</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 是一个用于备份和恢复 MySQL 或 MariaDB 数据库的命令行工具，可以生成包含 SQL 语句的文本文件，以便您可以轻松地将数据库导出到另一个系统或备份数据库。</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\" type=\"1\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\" value=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\">使用 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysqldump</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 导出数据库数据<br />执行以下命令以导出 MariaDB 数据库的数据：</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: inherit; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysqldump -u </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">root </span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: inherit; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">-p</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"> flame </span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: inherit; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">&gt; </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">db</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: inherit; color: #df3079; background: #F7F7F8;\">.sql</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #df3079;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\">其中 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">username</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 是 MariaDB 数据库用户的用户名，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">dbname</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 是要导出的数据库的名称，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">dbname.sql</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 是导出的 SQL 文件的名称和路径。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\">您需要输入 MariaDB 数据库用户的密码，以便 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysqldump</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 命令可以连接到数据库并导出数据。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\" type=\"1\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\" value=\"2\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\">使用 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysqldump</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 导出数据库结构和 SQL<br />要导出 MariaDB 数据库的结构和 SQL，执行以下命令：<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 9.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysqldump -u username -p --no-data dbname &gt; dbname_structure.sql</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\">这将导出 MariaDB 数据库的结构（即表、列、索引等），但不包含数据。<br />您需要输入 MariaDB 数据库用户的密码，以便 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysqldump</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 命令可以连接到数据库并导出数据。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"background: #F7F7F8;\">通过执行上述命令，您可以导出 MariaDB 数据库的数据和 SQL，并保存为文本文件。这些文件可以用于备份数据库，也可以用于将数据库迁移到另一个系统。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\" type=\"1\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\" value=\"8\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: #F7F7F8;\">没有权限</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\">MariaDB 在安装时会默认创建一个 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">root</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 用户，但它有两种身份：</span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">unix_socket</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 和 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysql_native_password</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\">如果您使用 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">unix_socket</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 身份验证插件进行身份验证，则 MariaDB 将使用操作系统的当前用户帐户来登录 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">root</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 用户，而不需要输入密码。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\">如果您使用 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysql_native_password</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 身份验证插件进行身份验证，则 MariaDB 将要求您输入 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">root</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 用户的密码，才能登录到 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">root</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 用户。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\">因此，如果您使用 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">unix_socket</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 身份验证插件进行身份验证，则可以使用 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">sudo</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 命令切换到 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">root</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 用户，并使用 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysql</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 命令登录到 MariaDB，而无需输入密码。但是，如果您使用 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysql_native_password</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 身份验证插件进行身份验证，则需要输入 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">root</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 用户的密码才能登录到 MariaDB。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\">要更改 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">root</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 用户的身份验证插件，请执行以下步骤：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\" type=\"i\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\" value=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">登录到 MariaDB：<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">css</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 9.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">Copy code<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysql -u root -p</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">使用以下命令查看 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">root</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 用户的身份验证插件：<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">sql</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 9.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">Copy code<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #2e95d3; background: #F7F7F8;\">SELECTUser</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">, Host, plugin </span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #2e95d3; background: #F7F7F8;\">FROM</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysql.user </span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #2e95d3; background: #F7F7F8;\">WHEREUser</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">=</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #00a67d; background: #F7F7F8;\">\'root\'</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">; <br /></span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">如果 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">plugin</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 列的值为 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">unix_socket</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">，则 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">root</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 用户将使用 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">unix_socket</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 身份验证插件进行身份验证。如果 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">plugin</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 列的值为 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysql_native_password</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">，则 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">root</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 用户将使用 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysql_native_password</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 身份验证插件进行身份验证。</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">如果需要更改身份验证插件，请使用以下命令更改 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">root</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 用户的身份验证插件：<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">sql</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 9.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">Copy code<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #2e95d3; background: #F7F7F8;\">UPDATE</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysql.user </span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #2e95d3; background: #F7F7F8;\">SET</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">plugin=</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #00a67d; background: #F7F7F8;\">\'mysql_native_password\'</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #2e95d3; background: #F7F7F8;\">WHEREUser</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">=</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #00a67d; background: #F7F7F8;\">\'root\'</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">; </span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">刷新权限：<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 9.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">Copy code<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">FLUSH PRIVILEGES; </span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">退出 MariaDB：<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">vbnet</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 9.0pt; color: #374151; background: #F7F7F8;\">Copy code<br /></span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #2e95d3; background: #F7F7F8;\">EXIT</span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #8f8f8f; background: #F7F7F8;\">; </span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: 1.125in; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\"><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\">现在，</span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">root</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 用户将使用 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">mysql_native_password</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 身份验证插件进行身份验证，因此您需要输入 </span><span style=\"font-family: \'S&ouml;hne Mono\'; background: #F7F7F8;\">root</span><span style=\"font-family: S&ouml;hne; background: #F7F7F8;\"> 用户的密码才能登录到 MariaDB。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #374151;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\" type=\"1\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\" value=\"9\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\">创建数据库并导入 sql 文件</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\">create database </span><span lang=\"en-US\">dbaname</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\">;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\">use </span><span lang=\"en-US\">dbaname</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\">; </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\">source </span><span lang=\"en-US\">xxx</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\">.sql;</span></p>\n</body>\n</html>',1,'在 Ubuntu 20.04 中，yum 命令不可用，因为它是 CentOS/RHEL 等 Red Hat 派生发行版中的软件包管理器。在 Ubuntu 中，您需要使用 apt 命令来安装','/upload/2023/2/70e1e5df6be84648aa1adeaf9ec6374f.png','使用Azure部署ubuntu 20.04',0,NULL),(18,'<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; border-width: 100%;\">\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; margin-top: 0in; margin-left: 0in; width: 8.9201in;\">\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; margin-top: 0in; margin-left: 0in; width: 8.9201in;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .375in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">安装 Java</p>\n<ul style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in;\">\n<ul style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in;\">\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\" type=\"a\">\n<li lang=\"en-US\" style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\" value=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\">Red hat</span></li>\n</ol>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span style=\"background: #F7F7F8;\">如果您正在使用 CentOS/RHEL 等基于 Red Hat 的发行版，可以使用以下命令安装 Java 1.8 开发包：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">yum&nbsp;&nbsp;install -y java-1.8.0-openjdk.x86_64</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">yum&nbsp;&nbsp;install -y java-1.8.0-openjdk-devel</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">sudo yum install -y java-1.8.0-openjdk-devel</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span style=\"background: #F7F7F8;\">这将安装 Java 1.8 开发包及其依赖项。安装完成后，您可以在系统中使用&nbsp;javac&nbsp;命令来编译 Java 程序。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ul style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in;\">\n<ul style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in;\">\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\" type=\"a\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\" value=\"2\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\">Ubuntu</span></li>\n</ol>\n</ul>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span style=\"background: #F7F7F8;\">要在 Ubuntu 中安装 OpenJDK 8，请执行以下命令：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #979797;\">sudo apt&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #2e95d3;\">update</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #979797;\">sudo apt install -y openjdk</span><span style=\"color: #df3079;\">-8</span><span style=\"color: #979797;\">-jdk</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span style=\"background: #F7F7F8;\">这将更新软件包列表并安装 OpenJDK 8。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span style=\"background: #F7F7F8;\">如果您想安装其他版本的 OpenJDK，请使用&nbsp;apt search openjdk&nbsp;命令搜索可用的 OpenJDK 包，然后使用&nbsp;apt install&nbsp;命令安装特定版本的 OpenJDK。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span style=\"background: #F7F7F8;\">请注意，Ubuntu 20.04 默认情况下不支持 OpenJDK 8，但是您可以添加 OpenJDK 8 的源以安装它。如果您使用的是 Ubuntu 20.04，请在安装 OpenJDK 8 之前，确保已添加 OpenJDK 8 的源。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span style=\"background: #F7F7F8;\">请注意，如果您使用的是 Ubuntu 或其他基于 Debian 的发行版，需要使用以下命令安装 Java 1.8 开发包：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span style=\"color: #979797;\">sudo apt&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #2e95d3;\">update</span><span style=\"color: #979797;\">sudo apt install -y openjdk</span><span style=\"color: #df3079;\">-8</span><span style=\"color: #979797;\">-jdk</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span style=\"background: #F7F7F8;\">这将安装 OpenJDK 8 开发包。同样，在安装完成后，您可以在系统中使用&nbsp;javac&nbsp;命令来编译 Java 程序。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .75in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; color: #595959;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ul style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in;\">\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\" type=\"a\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\" value=\"3\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\">使用命令 java -version 查看 jav</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\">a</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal;\">是否安装成功</span></li>\n</ol>\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;\" type=\"a\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle; font-weight: bold;\" value=\"4\"><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;\">jav</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;\">a -jar&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;\">xxx</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;\">.jar</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;\"> </span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;\">运行</span></li>\n</ol>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>',1,'安装 JavaRed hat如果您正在使用 CentOS/RHEL 等基于 Red Hat 的发行版，可以使用以下命令安装 Java 1.8 开发包：yum&nbsp','/upload/2023/2/7d3af57f78604ef99a88327e5779dff2.png','Azure 部署springboot',0,NULL),(19,'<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; border-width: 100%;\">\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; margin-top: 0in; margin-left: 0in; width: 7.343in;\">\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; margin-top: 0in; margin-left: 0in; width: 7.343in;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">Docker 是一个开源的容器技术，用于在虚拟环境中运行应用程序。它允许开发人员在一个轻量级的容器中打包应用程序及其依赖项，然后在任何平台上快速部署和运行这些容器。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">Docker 的主要功能包括：</p>\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12pt;\" type=\"1\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\" value=\"1\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">容器化应用程序：把应用程序和其依赖项打包到一个轻量级容器中，确保应用程序在任何环境中的一致性。</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">轻松部署和运行：快速部署和启动 Docker 容器，减少了在不同环境中的应用程序配置时间。</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">提高效率和可移植性：在同一个主机上运行多个独立的容器，避免资源冲突和版本问题。</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">提供一致的开发环境：开发人员可以使用 Docker 在任何环境中使用相同的开发环境，从而减少因环境不一致导致的问题。</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; margin-left: .375in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">总的来说，Docker 提供了一个快速、高效、可移植的容器技术，使应用程序在任何环境中都能够快速、可靠地运行。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Dockerfile如何运行</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">使用 Docker 运行 Dockerfile 的步骤如下：</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<ol style=\"direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12pt;\" type=\"1\">\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\" value=\"1\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">创建 Dockerfile：在终端或文本编辑器中创建一个名为 \"Dockerfile\" 的文件。</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">编写 Dockerfile：在 Dockerfile 中设置镜像的基础镜像、环境变量、文件以及命令等信息。</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">构建 Docker 镜像：运行 \"docker build\" 命令，指定 Dockerfile 的目录路径。</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; vertical-align: middle;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">启动 Docker 容器：运行 \"docker run\" 命令，指定构建的镜像名称。</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: 华文中宋; font-size: 12.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>',1,'Docker 是一个开源的容器技术，用于在虚拟环境中运行应用程序。它允许开发人员在一个轻量级的容器中打包应用程序及其依赖项，然后在任何平台上快速部署和运行这些容器。Docker 的主','/upload/2023/2/3a2e2a9a81cb46379e194a8e13d0e0ef.png','Docker到底是干什么的',0,NULL);
